r,Thai chilies, roasted coconut\ntraditional SAUTeés\nKung Pad Thai\nTiger Prawns saute with rice noodles, crispy egg crepe, ground peanuts, scallions,  bean sprouts, pickled radishes\nKai Siam\nCrispy Chicken breast,sweet chili sauce,onions,pineapple,cashew nuts,bell pepper,mushroom & scallions served with pineapple fried rice\nKra Pow Hoi\nJumbo Sea Scallops, sliced onions,green beans,bell peppers,Thai basil sauce\nChef Nan's Signature Specials\n-Market Price\nWhole Snapper 3 Flavor\nCrispy whole red Snapper,okra, eggplant & Chef Nan's signature three-flavored chili sauce served with jasmine rice\n-Market Price\n-Market Price\nLobster Pad Thai\nCrispy Lobster tail over rice noodles,egg crepe, crushed peanuts, scallions, bean sprouts, pickled radishes and lime\n-Market Price\nsea\n-Market Price\nPla Sahm Rod\nPan fried Chilean Sea bass, crispy okra,eggplant, Chef Nan's signature three- flavored chili sauce\n-Market Price\nPanang Talay\nPan-seared Tiger Prawns, scallops and calamari served with a mild Panang curry sauce with green beans\nPla Yang Prik Khing\nGrilled Salmon filet with sauteed green beans in a roasted red Thai curry sauce with crispy salmon flakes\nSiam Ruby\nPan-seared Sea Scallops in a spicy red curry, green beans, bamboo shoots and topped with Thai basil\nLand\n-Market Price\nGeah yang\nGrilled lamb chops with sweet soy coriander glaze, sweet \n\n--- Page: /s/NAN-FOODS-to-Print.pdf ---\n%PDF-1.7\n%����\n1 0 obj\n<\n>/Metadata 205 0 R/ViewerPreferences 206 0 R>>\nendobj\n2 0 obj\n<\n>\nendobj\n3 0 obj\n<\n>/ExtGState<\n>/Font<\n>/ProcSet[/PDF/Text/ImageB/ImageC/ImageI] >>/MediaBox[ 0 0 595.32 841.92] /Contents 4 0 R/Group<\n>/Tabs/S/StructParents 0>>\nendobj\n4 0 obj\n<\n>\nstream\nx��]k�\u001b9v�ހ��>\f��\u0002]�E�\u0010��=���z��b��\u0007g�u��=��\u0004A���dIU��%ʺ,1��=j�xx�����\n�ף��=�RZw�nTp��\u001b��Nٍ���v��O������GW�}\u0001�˿��ݯ_\u001e]=y����Ovs���GW��?�m6��en\\tv������At�yx�\u0018|�.l޾|tu����h�:�5|��r��_\u001e]��iDM\u001b�R�\"X�#\u0011�E;�\u000f�